        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer145108234" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11456252056444474604">Bought secondhand and devoured in a single overnight reading. Back in the day when I could do an overnight read - my rock and roll years.<br/><br/>Re-read and enjoyed a couple of times since.<br/><br/>An excellent read.</span>

