  <span id="freeText12879115228681778552" style="display:none">Stunning. A perfect literary accompaniment to my other WWI read, The Guns Of August. Much credit to translator Michael Glenny for conveying the deep thought and profound human feeling of Solzhenitsyn's work.</span>
